Package de.wwu.muggl.ui.gui.windows

Provides tha application's windows.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ShellWindow Interface to be implemented by all shell windows used in this GUI.
 

Class Summary
ArrayEntriesWindow The ArrayEntriesWindow is used to show alter the elements of arrays.
ClassInspectionWindow The ClassInspectionWindow shows a class in a tree view.
ClassPathEntriesWindow The ClassPathEntriesWindow shows the currently set class path entries.
ExecutionWindow The ExecutionWindow replaced the application's main window.
FastExecutionWindow The fast execution window is used in step by step execution mode.
GeneratorSelectionWindow This window is used to choose variable generators and array elements generators for the parameters of a method.
InputWindow Providing the small input window for the altering the values of primitive types, their wrappers and of Strings.
LogWindow This window shows the current log file of the application.
MethodParametersWindow This window is used to set the predefined parameters for a method.
OptionsWindow This window shows the options for the execution.
StepByStepExecutionWindow The StepByStepExecutionWindow allows the user to view the details of the execution of a program.
